Package: IsomorphismSim
Title: Simulation Framework for the Ant Colony / Random Forest Isomorphism
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ernest", "Fokoué", email = "epfeqa@rit.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Gregory", "Babbitt", email = "gabsbi@rit.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Yuval", "Levental", email = "yhl3051@rit.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides agent-based ant colony simulations, random forest variance
    decomposition experiments, and direct isomorphism tests demonstrating that
    social insect colonies and ensemble machine learning implement identical
    variance reduction strategies through decorrelation of identical units.
    Includes a Shiny app for interactive exploration.
